msgstr "Demonstrate how to maintain a complete conversation session:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:289
msgid "高级特性"
msgstr "Advanced features"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:291
msgid "SelfReference + runtime primitives"
msgstr "SelfReference + runtime primitives"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:293
msgid ""
"当挂载了带 runtime 的工具（例如 `PyRepl`）时，框架会在 system prompt 顶部注入一段去重后的工具最佳实践块；runtime"
" primitive 的指引会包含在这些工具自己的 best practices 中。"
msgstr ""
"When tools with runtime (e.g., `PyRepl`) are mounted, the framework will "
"inject a deduplicated block of tool best practices at the top of the system "
"prompt; guidance for runtime primitives will be included in these tools' own"
" best practices."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:295
msgid ""
"这段 guidance 会在每个回合按当前 runtime 状态重新构建，因此不会把临时运行时说明写进持久化 system-prompt "
"memory；需要持久修改提示词时，仍然使用 `set_system_prompt(...)` / "
"`append_system_prompt(...)`。"
msgstr ""
"This guidance will be rebuilt at each turn according to the current runtime "
"state, so it will not write temporary runtime instructions into the "
"persistent system-prompt memory; when you need to persistently modify the "
"prompt, still use `set_system_prompt(...)` / `append_system_prompt(...)`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:297
msgid "这段 guidance 会告诉 agent："
msgstr "This guidance will tell agent:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:299
msgid "如何发现当前挂载的 runtime 能力（`runtime.list_primitives()`）"
msgstr ""
"How to discover the currently mounted runtime capabilities "
"(`runtime.list_primitives()`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:300
msgid ""
"如何查看单个契约（`runtime.get_primitive_spec(name)`）或按条件筛选契约（`runtime.list_primitive_specs(names=[...],"
" contains=\"...\")`）"
msgstr ""
"How to view a single contract (`runtime.get_primitive_spec(name)`) or filter"
" contracts by condition (`runtime.list_primitive_specs(names=[...], "
"contains=\"...\")`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:301
msgid "如何查看 selfref 命名空间 guidance（`runtime.selfref.guide()`）"
msgstr "How to view selfref namespace guidance (`runtime.selfref.guide()`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:302
msgid "`reset_repl` 会清理 REPL 变量，并继续保留当前 runtime backend 状态"
msgstr ""
"`reset_repl` clears the REPL variables and continues to retain the current "
"runtime backend state"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:303
msgid "当绑定了 `SelfReference` 记忆时，本 chat 函数对应的 memory key 作用域"
msgstr ""
"The memory key scope corresponding to this chat function when "
"`SelfReference` memory is bound"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:305
msgid ""
"`PyRepl()` 默认会安装 builtin `selfref` pack；`llm_chat` 会直接从 toolkit 的 runtime "
"backend 解析并复用这份默认 backend。"
msgstr ""
"`PyRepl()` will install the builtin `selfref` pack by default; `llm_chat` "
"will directly parse and reuse this default backend from the toolkit's "
"runtime backend."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:307
msgid "示例："
msgstr "Example:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:326
msgid "单次调用的高级覆盖（可选）："
msgstr "Advanced override for single call (optional):"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:338
msgid "在 `execute_code` 中，优先通过 runtime primitives 处理记忆："
msgstr ""
"In `execute_code`, prioritize handling memory through runtime primitives:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:346
msgid "Runtime self-reference 原语参考："
msgstr "Runtime self-reference Primitive Reference:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:348
msgid "`runtime.selfref.guide()`: 返回命名空间概览与 fork / 记忆最佳实践清单。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.guide()`: Returns namespace overview and fork/memory best "
"practices checklist."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:349
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.keys()`: 列出所有已绑定的 memory key。"
msgstr "`runtime.selfref.history.keys()`: List all bound memory keys."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:350
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.active_key()`: 获取当前上下文解析出的 active key。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.active_key()`: Gets the active key parsed from the "
"current context."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:351
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.count(key=None)`: 返回解析后 key 的消息数量。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.count(key=None)`: Returns the number of messages "
"for the parsed key."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:352
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.all(key=None)`: 返回完整消息列表的深拷贝。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.all(key=None)`: Returns a deep copy of the complete"
" message list."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:353
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.get(index, key=None)`: 读取指定索引的消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.get(index, key=None)`: Read the message at the "
"specified index."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:354
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.append(message, key=None)`: 追加一条消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.append(message, key=None)`: append a message."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:355
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.insert(index, message, key=None)`: 在指定索引插入一条消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.insert(index, message, key=None)`: Insert a message"
" at the specified index."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:356
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.update(index, message, key=None)`: 替换指定索引消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.update(index, message, key=None)`: Replace the "
"message at the specified index."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:357
msgid "`runtime.selfref.history.delete(index, key=None)`: 删除指定索引消息。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.delete(index, key=None)`: Delete the message at the"
" specified index."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:358
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(messages, key=None)`: 用校验后的消息列表替换整段历史。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(messages, key=None)`: Replace the entire "
"history with the validated message list."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:359
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.clear(key=None)`: 清理非 system 消息并保留当前 system prompt。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.clear(key=None)`: Clear non-system messages and "
"keep the current system prompt."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:360
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.get_system_prompt(key=None)`: 读取最新 system prompt。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.get_system_prompt(key=None)`: Read the latest "
"system prompt."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:361
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.set_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: 覆盖当前 system "
"prompt。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.set_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: Overwrites the "
"current system prompt."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:362
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.append_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: 向现有 system "
"prompt memory 追加文本。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.history.append_system_prompt(text, key=None)`: Appends text"
" to the existing system prompt memory."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:363
msgid "`runtime.selfref.fork.spawn(message, ...)`: 异步创建子 self-fork（chat 形态）。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.fork.spawn(message, ...)`: Asynchronously create child "
"self-fork (chat form)."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:364
msgid ""
"`runtime.selfref.fork.gather_all(fork_id_or_list=None, "
"include_history=False)`: 聚合 fork 结果，返回 `dict[fork_id -> ForkResult]`（用 "
"`.items()` / `.values()` 遍历）。"
msgstr ""
"`runtime.selfref.fork.gather_all(fork_id_or_list=None, "
"include_history=False)`: Aggregate fork results, returns `dict[fork_id -> "
"ForkResult]` (traverse using `.items()` / `.values()`)."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_chat.md:366
msgid ""
"默认情况下 fork 结果是紧凑模式（`history_included=False`，并提供 `history_count` "
"元数据），这样主上下文可以保持简洁。 确实需要完整子历史时，再显式使用 `include_history=True`。"
msgstr ""
"By default, the fork result is in compact mode (`history_included=False`, "
"and provides `history_count` metadata), so that the main context can stay "
"concise.  When you really need the complete sub-history, then explicitly use"
" `include_history=True`."

